popt4jlib.PS
Interface ChromosomeVelocityAdderIntf

All Known Implementing Classes:
DblArray1ChromosomeVelocityAdder
public interface ChromosomeVelocityAdderIntf

class specifies the operator for adding velocity objects to chromosome objects, with the help of some parameters specified in a HashMap. When both objects are arrays of same length, clearly the operator amounts to creating a new array whose elements are the sum of the corresponding elements of the two arrays; in other cases, the "addition" operation would be more complex, and the corresponding class will implement the specification.
